    In Alsace, and more particularly at the Klipfel domain, wine is a matter of family. Successive generations have maintained passion, love for the soil, rigor, consistency and loyalty since 1824. You are welcome to join us for a tasting (3 to 5 wines) and severals explainations on the alsacian vineyard and our know-how specifically by us, at the Estate Klipfel. Visiting the old cellars and viticulture museum is possible ONLY AFTER RESERVATION. Please contact us per email at least 10 days before your visit so that we can make an appointment.
